  ('buttress', 'v.', '支持、加強', 'SUPPORT, STRENGTHEN // n. support built against a wall .', 'The new evidence helped to buttress the case against the suspect. 新的證據有助於支持針對嫌疑人的指控。', array['bolster', 'brace', 'carry', 'shore (up)', 'support', 'sustain', 'undergird', 'uphold']::text[], '{}'::text[], '跌倒時屁股(butt)是很好的支撐', 3, 3, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 50'),
