  ('circumscribe', 'v.', '限制', 'restrict (sth) within limits; confine', 'Nevertheless, under the anti-Jewish policies of the Nazis, his father’s academic career became circumscribed. 在納粹的反猶太 政策下，他爸爸的學術生涯變得受限', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], 'circum(環繞) + scribe(寫) → 畫地為牢 → 限制', 5, 5, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 7'),
