  ('compatible', 'adj.', '和諧共處的、相容的', '(of people, ideas, arguments, principles, etc) suited; that can exist together', 'This printer is compatible with most PCs. 這印表機與多數PC相容 // The careers structure here is not compatible with having a family 本地的職涯結構與扶養家庭不相容', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], 'com(共同) + pat(感情) + ible → 有共同感情的 → 相容的', 5, 5, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 13'),
