  ('compelling', 'adj.', '令人注目的、極端吸引人的；強制的；強而有力的', 'extremely interesting and exciting, so that one has to pay attention', 'The novel was so compelling that I couldn''t put it down. // no compelling evidence 強而有力的證據', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 4, 4, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 17'),
