  ('concede', 'v.', '承認、讓步', 'to acknowledge grudgingly or hesitantly; to relinquish grudgingly or hesitantly; to accept as true, valid or accurate', 'The candidate conceded that he had lost the election. 這位候選人承認他已經在競選中失敗。 It is impossible for us to concede to your unreasonable request. 要我們對你的無理要求讓步是不可能的。They conceded us the right to cross their land. 他們容許我 們在他們的土地上有過路權。', array['acknowledge', 'accept', 'allow', 'grant 承認 n. concession 讓步']::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 5, 5, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 12'),
