  ('conciliatory', 'adj.', '撫慰的、調和的', 'intended to gain goodwill or favor or to reduce hostility', 'speaking in a conciliatory tone 用一個和解的、調和的語調說話', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 4, 4, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 20'),
