  ('condescending', null, '傲慢的、恩賜的、屈尊的', null, 'Will her doctor give her a condescending lecture, or gently persuade her to cut her alcohol intake? 醫師會高傲區尊地指導她，還 是溫柔的說服她減少飲酒？ a condescending smile 高傲的笑', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 5, 5, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 11'),
