  ('congenial', 'adj.', '意氣相投的、性情好的', 'pleasing because of similarities in temperament, interests,etc', 'I met few people congenial to me in that city. 我在那個城市沒有遇到幾個意氣相投的', array['agreeable', 'pleasing', 'compatible', 'harmonious']::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 5, 5, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 13'),
