  ('consistent', 'adj.', '始終如一的、前後一致的', '(of a person, his behaviour, his views, etc) always keeping to the same pattern or style; unchanging', 'a consistent style in writing 一個始終如一的寫作風格', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 5, 5, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 14'),
  ('consolidate', 'v.', '鞏固、堅強；合併', 'become more solid, secure, or strong; merge', 'The company consolidated its position in the international market 公司鞏固了自己在國際市場的位置 // The two companies consolidated. 兩間公司合併', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 4, 4, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 17'),
