  ('conspicuous', 'adj.', '顯著的、顯而易見的', 'easily seen; noticeable; remarkable', 'The chicken has a conspicuous red head. 這隻雞有很顯著的紅頭', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], 'con(共同) + spic(看) + uous → 都能看到的 → 顯而易見的', 5, 5, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 14'),
