  ('constrain', 'v.', '強迫、迫使', 'make (sb) do sth by strong (moral) persuasion or by force', null, '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 3, 3, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 46'),
  ('construe', 'v.', '解釋、理解為', 'sth (fml ) explain the meaning of (words, sentences, actions, etc); interpret sth', 'The vanquished manage to construe the victor’s triumph as the result of some spurious advantage, the victors being truly inferior where it counts.', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 3, 3, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 46'),
