  ('contentious', 'adj.', '有爭議的；好辯的', 'likely to cause disagreement or argument; exhibiting an often perverse and wearisome tendency to quarrels and disputes', 'climate change legislation remained contentious 氣候變遷立法仍是有爭議的', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], 'contend 主張 + ous 多…的', 5, 5, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 4'),
