  ('corroborate', 'v.', '證實、確證', 'confirm or give support to', 'Studies that are wrong will be superseded 代替，取代 by better studies with different results. Studies that are right will be corroborated by other good studies. - Harriet Hall, Skeptic, 2007', array['a. corroborative 確證的']::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 5, 5, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 8'),
