  ('decry', 'v.', '責難、誹謗', 'sb/sth (as sth) speak critically of sb/sth to make him/it seem less valuable, useful, etc; disparage sb/sth', 'In her article, she decries the pollution of the environment by manufacturers.', array['denigrate', 'deprecate']::text[], array['acclaim', 'applaud']::text[], 'de(向外) + cry(叫、哭) → 半夜大吼大叫要譴責 → 譴責', 4, 4, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 32'),
