  ('defy', 'v.', '反抗、違抗、蔑視', 'disobey or refuse to respect (sb, an authority, etc)', 'defy a court order 違抗法庭命令 // defied her parents 反抗父母 // Some Southern California business owners will defy governor’ s coronavirus shutdown order.', array['a. defiant 挑釁的', '目中無人的']::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 4, 4, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 32'),
