  ('delude', 'v.', '欺騙、哄騙', 'sb deliberately mislead sb; deceive sb', 'We deluded ourselves into thinking that the ice cream wouldn''t affect our diet. 我們哄騙自己相信冰淇淋部會影響我們的節食 // He deluded everyone into following him. 他騙得大家都跟隨他', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 4, 4, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 22'),
