  ('equilibrium', 'n.', '平衡', 'state of being balanced', 'But longer dry seasons, the expansion of the desert and one of the world’s fastest-growing populations, has destroyed that equilibrium. 乾季的延長、沙漠的擴張和全球最快的人口成長摧毀了平衡', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 3, 3, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 37'),
