  ('erratic', 'adj.', '飄忽不定的；反覆無常的、古怪的', 'irregular or uneven in movement, quality or behaviour; unreliable', 'an erratic comet 飄忽不定的彗星 // an erratic genius 一個古怪的天才', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 4, 4, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 27'),
