  ('impede', 'v.', '妨礙、阻礙、阻止', 'hinder or obstruct the progress or movement of', 'The attempt to rescue the climbers was impeded by bad weather. 救援登山者的努力因天氣惡劣而受阻', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 5, 5, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 13'),
  ('impel', 'v.', '推進、推動', 'sb (to sth) force or urge sb to do sth', 'He said he had been impelled to crime by poverty. 他說貧困逼得他犯罪', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 1, 1, 'Mason 2000 / Mason 2000 PDF page 62 / 字根 pel 推、逐、驅 / 提示 compel 強迫'),
  ('impending', 'adj.', '即將發生的、逼近的', 'about to happen; imminent', '(volcano''s) impending eruption', array['brew', 'loom']::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 2, 2, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 62'),
  ('impenetrable', 'adj.', '不能通過的、不能穿透的；不能理解的', 'that cannot be entered, passed through, etc', 'Armor plate is impenetrable by ordinary bullets. 裝甲板普通子彈打不穿 // The motive for the crime was impenetrable. 那起罪行 的作案動機叫人捉摸不透', '{}'::text[], array['penetrable']::text[], null, 4, 4, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 19'),
  ('imperative', 'adj.', '必要的、緊急的、極重要的', 'very urgent or important; needing immediate attention', 'It is imperative that standards are maintained. 標準被維持是至關重要的 // "Eat your rice!" is an imperative sentence. 祈使句', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 4, 4, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 21'),
  ('imperil', 'v.', '使陷於危險、危及', '(fml ) put (sb/sth) in danger; endanger', 'could imperil human civilization 將危害整個人類文明', array['compromise', 'endanger', 'hazard', 'jeopard', 'jeopardize', 'menace', 'peril', 'risk', 'venture']::text[], '{}'::text[], '近 peril(致命危險), perish(毀滅)', 3, 3, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 52'),
  ('imperious', 'adj.', '傲慢的、專橫的', 'proud and arrogant; domineering; expecting obedience', 'imperious style', array['despotic', 'dictatorial', 'overbearing', 'tyrannical']::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 2, 2, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 59'),
  ('impermanent', 'adj.', '不持久的、暫時的', 'not permanent; temporary', null, '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 1, 1, 'Mason 2000 / Mason 2000 PDF page 47 / 字根 man, main 停留 / 提示 remain 剩下、留下'),
