  ('incursion', 'n.', '入侵；侵略', '(into/on/upon sth) sudden attack on or invasion of a place (not usu made in order to occupy it permanently)', 'balloon incursion 氣球入侵', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 1, 1, 'Mason 2000 / Mason 2000 PDF page 22 / 字根 cur, cour 跑、短 / 提示 cursor 游標'),
