  ('indict', 'v.', '控訴、起訴', 'sb (law ) accuse sb officially (of sth); charge sb', 'A grand jury is expected to indict him for murder. 謀殺罪名起訴', array['accuse', 'charge', 'impeach', 'incriminate']::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 1, 1, 'Mason 2000 / Mason 2000 PDF page 24 / 字根 dic, dict 說話、命令 / 提示 predict 預測'),
  ('indifferent', 'adj.', '漠不關心的', 'having no interest in sb/sth; neither for nor against sb/sth; not caring about sb/sth', 'She was indifferent to the news of her ex-boyfriend''s engagement. 她對前男友訂婚的消息毫不在意。', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 3, 3, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 52'),
