  ('indigent', 'adj.', '貧困的、貧窮的', 'poor', 'The organization provides free meals to indigent families in the community. 該組織向社區中的貧困家庭提供免費的餐食。', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], 'in(=not) + dig(挖 → 錢包挖不出錢 → 貧困的', 1, 1, 'Mason 2000 / Mason 2000 PDF page 111 / 字根 vulg 普通 / 提示 vulgar 粗俗的、下流的'),
  ('indignant', 'adj.', '憤怒的、憤慨的', '(at/over/about sth) angry and scornful, esp at injustice or because of undeserved blame, etc', 'He was very indignant about the changes. 對於這些改變相當憤怒 an indignant tone of voice', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 1, 1, 'Mason 2000 / Mason 2000 PDF page 23 / 字根 dain, dign 高貴的 / 提示 dignity 尊嚴、莊嚴'),
