  ('indulgent', 'adj.', '縱容的、溺愛的', 'willing to allow excessive leniency, generosity, or consideration', 'She was perhaps a bit too indulgent with her children. 她可能對她小孩有點過於縱容', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 4, 4, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 19'),
