  ('inexorable', 'adj.', '不為所動的、堅決不變的', 'continuing unstoppably; relentless', '<We cannot stop the inexorable passing of time.> <The Inexorable Rise Of Amazon: Nine Reasons Why It''ll Only Get Bigger>', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], 'in(不) + ex(出) + ora(說) + ble → 說不動', 3, 3, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 42'),
  ('inexplicable', 'adj.', '無法說明的、難以理解的、莫名其妙的', 'that cannot be explained', 'an inexplicable disappearance 難以理解的消失 // an inexplicable desire for ice cream at two in the morning 在凌晨兩點無法解 釋的對冰淇淋的渴望', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 5, 5, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 14'),
