  ('inhibit', 'v.', '約束、壓抑、抑制', 'sb prevent sb from doing sth that should be natural or easy to do', 'You shouldn''t allow fear of failure to inhibit you. 你不能讓失敗的恐懼約束你', array['encumber', 'hamper', 'hold back', 'impede', 'manacle', 'obstruct', 'shackle', 'stymie', 'tie up']::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 5, 5, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 15'),
