  ('inquisitive', 'adj.', '好奇的、愛鑽研的', 'fond of inquiring into other people''s affairs', 'As a child, she was always very inquisitive, constantly asking questions about the world around her. 她小時候就非常好奇，總是詢 問對周遭的世界的問題。', array['curious', 'nosy', 'prying', 'snoopy']::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 3, 3, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 52'),
