  ('nominal', 'adj.', '名義上的、有名無實的', 'existing, etc in name only; not real or actual', 'U.S. revises up nominal 2018 GDP 美國上調2018名目GDP', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 4, 4, 'Mason 2000 / Mason 2000 PDF page 56 / 字根 nomin, nom 名稱、名字 / 提示 nominal 名義上的'),
  ('nonchalant', 'adj.', '無憂無慮的、漠不關心的', 'not feeling or showing interest or enthusiasm; calm and casual', 'Wen Beyoncé floating stage malfunctioned, Beyoncé remained nonchalant, blowing kisses to the fans below. 舞台故障時，Beyonc é仍然毫不在意，持續對觀眾給予飛吻', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 2, 2, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 55'),
  ('nonpareil', 'n.', '無匹敵的', 'adj (person or thing) without an equal or rival', null, '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], 'non(沒有) + par(平等) + eil', 2, 1, 'Mason 2000 / Mason 2000 PDF page 59 / 字根 par 平等 / 提示 compare 比較'),
  ('normative', 'adj.', '標準的；規範的；合乎規範的、按規定準則的', 'describing or setting standards or rules of language, behaviour, etc, which should be followed', 'The normative approach to ethics emphasizes the importance of moral principles and standards in guiding behavior. 道德規範方法 強調道德原則和標準在指導行為中的重要性。', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 3, 3, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 41'),
  ('nostalgia', 'n.', '思鄉病', 'sentimental longing for things that are past', 'A wave of nostalgia swept over me when I saw my childhood school.', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], 'nost(家) + alg (痛) + ia', 4, 4, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 26'),
  ('nostrum', 'n.', '家傳秘方、江湖藥、萬靈丹', 'medicine falsely recommended as effective; quack remedy', null, '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 1, 1, 'Mason 2000 / Mason 2000 PDF page 56 / 字根 nost 家 / 提示 nostalgia 鄉愁'),
