  ('orthodontics', 'n.', '齒科矯正術、正牙學（作單數用）', '(branch of dentistry that deals with) preventing and correcting irregularities in the position of the teeth and jaws', null, '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], 'ortho(正) dont(=dent 牙齒) + ics', 5, 2, 'Mason 2000 / Mason 2000 PDF page 26 / 字根 dog, dox 觀點、思想 / 提示 dogma 教條、教義'),
  ('orthodox', 'adj.', '正統的、傳統的、習俗的、通常的', 'conforming to established doctrine especially in religion; CONVENTIONAL', 'orthodox religion 正統宗教 orthodox views/opinions 正統觀點', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], 'ortho(正) + dox(思想)', 5, 5, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 5'),
  ('oscillate', 'v.', '擺動、搖擺', 'move repeatedly and regularly from one position to another and back again', 'The stock market has been oscillating between gains and losses for the past week. 股市在過去一周內一直在漲跌之間搖擺不 定。', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 1, 1, 'Mason 2000 / Mason 2000 PDF page 115 / 字根 vulg 普通 / 提示 vulgar 粗俗的、下流的'),
