  ('overbearing', 'adj.', '專橫的、好指使人的、傲慢的；至關重要的', 'forcing others to do what one wants (without caring about their feelings); domineering; decisively important : DOMINANT', 'one "overbearing" woman has sparked furious debate online after she revealed she has restricted her boyfriend''s gaming habit to just "one hour per day". - Lydia Hawken', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 3, 3, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 53'),
