  ('palpable', 'adj.', '可觸知的、可摸到的、極其明瞭的', 'that can be felt or touched', 'The frustration at the sluggish acceptance of Covid vaccines has been palpable in Russia, with President Vladimir Putin making numerous attempts to extol the benefits of the vaccine to the reticent public. - CNBC', array['tangible']::text[], array['subtle(難以捉摸的', '微妙的)']::text[], null, 2, 2, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 61'),
