  ('sanctimonious', 'adj.', '道貌岸然；假裝虔誠的、假裝聖潔的', 'hypocritically pious or devout; acting as if morally better than others; showing that you believe you are morally better, or more religious', 'santimonious right-wing media 道貌岸然的右翼媒體 // sanctimonious liberals 自由派', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], 'sanct(神聖的) + moni(音讀模擬) → 模擬神聖的 → 假裝虔誠的', 3, 3, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 45'),
