  ('seminal', 'adj.', '開創性的、種子的、有發展性的', 'containing or contributing the seeds of later development : CREATIVE, ORIGINAL', 'Einstein''s theory of relativity was a seminal contribution to the field of physics. 愛因斯坦相對論對當代物理學有開創性影響', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 1, 1, 'Mason 2000 / Mason 2000 PDF page 77 / 字根 semin 種子 / 提示 seminar 研討會'),
