  ('serendipitous', null, '意外發現的', null, 'unning into my old friend at the airport was a serendipitous encounter. 在機場偶然遇到舊朋友是一次意外的相遇。', '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], 'The name is from Serendip, an old name for Ceylon (modern Sri Lanka), from Arabic Sarandib, from Sanskrit Simhaladvipa "Dwelling-Place-of-Lions Island."', 3, 3, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 54'),
