  ('stanch', 'v.', '使傷口止血、止住', 'stop the flow of (esp blood)', null, '{}'::text[], '{}'::text[], null, 1, 1, 'Mason 2000 / Mason 2000 PDF page 82 / 字根 sta, st 站 / 提示 obstacle 障礙、干擾'),
