  ('treacherous', 'adj.', '危險的；背叛的；不可靠的', 'likely to betray trust : UNRELIABLE; marked by hidden dangers, hazards, or perils', 'Russian rockets are forcing many Ukrainian to leave behind loved ones who can''t make the treacherous journey out of the country. 俄 羅斯戰爭迫使烏克蘭人離開他們無法踏上當難民的險峻旅程的親人', array['perfidious(背叛的)', 'unreliable(不可靠的)']::text[], '{}'::text[], '音讀「踹老師」 → 背叛的、危險的', 4, 4, 'Mason 1000; Mason 2000 / primary: Mason 1000 PDF page 24'),
